-- GM says Chevy Volt still on track for 2010 launch
-- 
-- Sun Jan 11, 2009 12:47pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/01/11/us-gm-volt-sb-idUSTRE50A22L20090111

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - General Motors Corp ( GM.N ) said on Sunday that its Chevy Volt is still on track for a 2010 launch. 

 Highlights: * Vice Chairman Bob Lutz says GM has growing confidence lithium-ion battery technology is 'reliable' * Vice Chairman Lutz says U.S. economic stimulus package 'absolutely matters' for auto industry * Vice Chairman Lutz says U.S. economic stimulus package could include 'heavy federal incentives' for buying fuel-efficient vehicles